OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear night ahead with a light breeze.
OL,7,FThis will allow temperatures to
OL,8,Fquickly drop, and fall close to
OL,9,Ffreezing in sheltered rural locations,
OL,10,Fleading to a patchy frost. Mist and
OL,11,Ffog patches forming in the east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,14,Fto start the weekend. Sunshine could
OL,15,Fturn hazy at times in places, but will
OL,16,Ffeel very warm in the light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
